(HubSpot)\n\nhubspot — `search` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Diff the Two Systems · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 HubSpot private-app token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,250],"id":"dc206f6b-930d-5020-5c01-e812dd137c9d","name":"Note: Pull Side A (HubSpot)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Pull Side B (Google Sheets)\n\ngoogleSheets — `read` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Diff the Two Systems · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,790],"id":"99157bf7-153c-b6dc-ae28-7ca2304691f6","name":"Note: Pull Side B (Google Sheets)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Diff the Two Systems\n\nDiffs two streams by key into 4 lanes: only-in-A, same, different, only-in-B — the heart of the sync.\n\nPorts: ①→ Create Missing in Google Sheets · ②→ Count In-Sync Rows · ③→ Apply Updates to Google Sheets · ④→ Backfill into HubSpot","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,520],"id":"d61ad2c8-d12e-8f58-ae49-aab14a59b00f","name":"Note: Diff the Two Systems"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Create Missing in Google Sheets\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Gather Sync Results · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1938,-80],"id":"4a7abf57-7a25-7d8a-a98a-c0f0802d67d9","name":"Note: Create Missing in Google Sheets"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Count In-Sync Rows\n\nCollapses all items into a single summary item (for counts and run stats).\n\nNext: Gather Sync Results","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2262,340],"id":"3bef5b54-d069-5a9a-9537-8f1ef80d1bb3","name":"Note: Count In-Sync Rows"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Apply Updates to Google Sheets\n\ngoogleSheets — `appendOrUpdate` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Gather Sync Results · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2586,760],"id":"cce1c3c6-b2ea-255b-5dec-a99c99ff6262","name":"Note: Apply Updates to Google Sheets"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Backfill into HubSpot\n\nhubspot — `contact` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Gather Sync Results · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 HubSpot private-app token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2910,1180],"id":"ca00c043-a810-75c7-7f4c-3e46a0b093f4","name":"Note: Backfill into HubSpot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Gather Sync Results\n\nRejoins 4 branches into one stream (mode: append) so downstream logic runs once.\n\nNext: Guard Non-Empty type","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3558,520],"id":"0fed2bb7-a2bb-9705-2fbc-f80f994a424c","name":"Note: Gather Sync Results"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Guard Non-Empty type\n\nDrops items that fail the condition; only qualifying items continue (no false branch).\n\nNext: Tag Pipeline Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4530,520],"id":"47b886f8-7067-473a-633c-42fbbdb6d96c","name":"Note: Guard Non-Empty type"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Tag Pipeline Metadata\n\nShapes the item: writes `pipeline`, `version`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Stamp Processing Time","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4854,520],"id":"209f2826-1929-78af-1c83-bcf99aaca4ff","name":"Note: Tag Pipeline Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp Processing Time\n\nStamps `processedAt` with the current time for auditing.\n\nNext: Cap Batch Volume","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5178,520],"id":"42e2bd42-b084-0a62-aa8c-2dd4e7f74cee","name":"Note: Stamp Processing Time"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Cap Batch Volume\n\nCaps the stream at 25 items to protect downstream quotas.\n\nNext: Sort Jobs Newest First","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5502,520],"id":"9e67d876-85b4-ed7b-1c4f-cdb55efee070","name":"Note: Cap Batch Volume"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Sort Jobs Newest First\n\nOrders items (newest first) so limits and digests pick the most relevant records.\n\nNext: Summarize Run Stats","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5826,520],"id":"4ae52839-4a99-91b0-44bc-f45bf5243d33","name":"Note: Sort Jobs Newest First"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6150,520],"id":"96c7d2d1-3fc6-164c-7ca3-f09345f77b85","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Slack · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6474,520],"id":"1a2fa58f-3d95-b26e-0d52-3f292cadc47b","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6798,520],"id":"9be2605c-e6d2-6e69-fba6-5908878edc4c","name":"Note: Send Summary to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Microsoft Teams","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6150,1540],"id":"e5c121a1-3371-bb3e-eeb7-77c8ec33ab56","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Microsoft Teams\n\nmicrosoftTeams — `chatMessage` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Microsoft OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6474,1540],"id":"fde2e565-e519-8914-29b3-dd0a65bed76b","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Microsoft Teams"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Sync contacts across systems with HubSpot and Google Sheets and log the results\n\n**Pattern:** Two-System Sync · **Level:** Advanced · **Trigger:** Scheduled\n\n## What it does\nSync contacts across systems with HubSpot and Google Sheets and log the results. It runs automatically on a schedule.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual utilities is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nDaily Schedule → Pull Side A (HubSpot) → Diff the Two Systems → Create Missing in Google Sheets → Gather Sync Results → Guard Non-Empty type → Tag Pipeline Metadata → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to two-system sync without manual effort\n- Anyone automating utilities in productivity\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Improves response time\n- Has retries and error handling built in\n- Saves hours of manual work each week\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: Google OAuth2 / service account; HubSpot private-app token; Microsoft OAuth2; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"2b59618b-c276-e3cc-f824-a0f25707e875","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-620],"id":"809ba1b9-c5b6-6b6a-9f60-0999a8eb5452","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🧹 Data quality\n\nDedupe/diff steps make re-runs safe: the same input twice will not create duplicate records. If you change the key fields, clear n8n's dedupe memory (node → 'Clear stored keys') before the next run.","width":360,"height":260,"color":1},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-620],"id":"4a08c2e6-dfc4-c28b-b9b1-4418409f3390","name":"🧹 Data quality"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your utilities process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[610,-620],"id":"39d24def-2b02-4d27-faf0-085fe3d7f89c","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"Daily Schedule":{"main":[[{"node":"Pull Side A (HubSpot)","type":"main","index":0},{"node":"Pull Side B (Google Sheets)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Pull Side A (HubSpot)":{"main":[[{"node":"Diff the Two Systems","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Pull Side B (Google Sheets)":{"main":[[{"node":"Diff the Two Systems","type":"main","index":1}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Diff the Two Systems":{"main":[[{"node":"Create Missing in Google Sheets","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Count In-Sync Rows","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Apply Updates to Google Sheets","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Backfill into HubSpot","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Create Missing in Google Sheets":{"main":[[{"node":"Gather Sync Results","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Count In-Sync Rows":{"main":[[{"node":"Gather Sync Results","type":"main","index":1}]]},"Apply Updates to Google Sheets":{"main":[[{"node":"Gather Sync Results","type":"main","index":2}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Backfill into HubSpot":{"main":[[{"node":"Gather Sync Results","type":"main","index":3}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Gather Sync Results":{"main":[[{"node":"Guard Non-Empty type","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Guard Non-Empty type":{"main":[[{"node":"Tag Pipeline Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Tag Pipeline Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp Processing Time","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp Processing Time":{"main":[[{"node":"Cap Batch Volume","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Cap Batch Volume":{"main":[[{"node":"Sort Jobs Newest First","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Sort Jobs Newest First":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Run Stats","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Summarize Run Stats":{"main":[[{"node":"Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Slack","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Microsoft Teams","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Slack":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"1aebe880-f2eb-41bc-b082-4481e3b061f9","id":"FDX06307"}